descriptionHtml:
RVUniverse is your one-stop resource for buying and selling all kinds of new and used RVs, including Class A, B, B+, C, and Super C motorhomes, fifth wheel trailers, truck campers, travel trailers, toy haulers, teardrop trailers, pop-up campers, park models, and more. The RVUniverse app brings the world of RVUniverse to your Android mobile devices!
- Find new and used RVs for sale near you
- Browse motorhomes & trailers based on category, make, or model
- Use powerful search and filtering to find the exact RV you need
- Find parts and RV components quickly with a dedicated search feature
- View photos and videos of RVs inside and out
- Tap to contact sellers directly
- Get map directions to an RV’s location
- Apply for financing at competitive rates
- Get fast quotes for transporting RVs

Register to unlock extra features!
- Create a private Watch List and track RVs on all your devices
- Post a free Want To Buy to see if dealers have what you need
- Consign your RV or sell it yourself
- Receive alerts and weekly updates so you don’t miss the latest RVs for sale

Are you an RV dealer? Add new inventory, specify prices, upload photos and videos, and watch your RVs appear on the RVUniverse app and RVUniverse.com—all from your Android device.

RVUniverse features a continuously updated database of equipment, parts, and accessories for sale directly from dealers’ inventories.

RVUniverse has thousands of listings for RVs for sale from coast to coast, plus hundreds of RV parts and components. You’ll find new and used RVs from Airstream, Coachmen, Dutchmen, Forest River, Grand Design, Heartland, Jayco, Keystone RV, Palomino, Thor Motor Coach, Winnebago, and other manufacturers.

RVUniverse is a product of Sandhills Global, the company behind Machinery Trader, Truck Paper, TractorHouse, MotorSportsUniverse, AuctionTime, and many other brands serving buyers and sellers in the construction, agriculture, trucking, and aviation industries.
